metadata.name: FROGGER #001
metadata.description:
We all play a variety of roles in real life, but the majority of them require us to respond to society or those we care about. Besides, being "Frogger" reflects real freedom of imagination; there is no need to care about the world; simply let it flow and play by ears. Make the most of your soul by unleashing your creativity.

*I love Pepe's character, and his meme inspired me.

Artwork information : 
2000 x 2000 Pixel
3s Animation Loop
30 FPS | MP4 H264
Stereo (L R)
